    "For analysis, the feature extraction model without Higuchi FD offers the reduced performance values compared to the integration of all FD features.",
    "Hence, it is stated that the incorporation of all FD features could efficiently improves the performance of entire seizure detection system.",
    "Depending on how the epileptic seizure manifests itself, there are various categories into which it can be divided.",
    "The ictal state refers to the period between the beginning of the seizure and its conclusion.",
    "After a seizure has ended, a postictal state begins and lasts for a short while."
